{"tid":360142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好友紋身悼慘死情侶","createTime":"2017-08-15T05:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T12:01:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eef95a1883e6ef0ae729492bd09e0a91e49084f1","tid":360142,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20121979&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20121979%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170815&d=aQcvaE3XEPnkTHhprgLkAo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4646ed21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20121979%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170815&h=d0c55b2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20121979&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170815</a><br />\n<br />\n好友紋身悼慘死情侶<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌美適工業大廈3死奪命火警，政府化驗師在現場未有撿獲磷粉等易燃物品，但發現存有不少酒精類飲品，警方不排除有人玩「火燄調酒」期間，火燄燃起隔音綿肇禍，但真相仍有待調查。3名死者的親友昨到現場拜祭，好友亦在網上悼念，其中一名與慘死情侶陸漢賢和鄭詩敏十分要好的少女阿婷，更在自己的手背紋上二人的死忌日子，並將照片上載facebook作悼念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170815/large/a0701b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170815%2Flarge%2Fa0701b.gif&h=bc95606b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有好友將死者忌日紋於手背，以作悼念。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n逾50親友到現場拜祭<br />\n<br />\n3名死者陸漢賢（25歲）、蕭澤新（18歲）及鄭詩敏（21歲），他們的家人昨晨到殮房認屍後，下午各自帶同道士到火場拜祭，聯同親友合共50多人。親友分批進入現場拜祭，道士作招魂儀式，拜祭歷時約3句鐘，離去時各人神情哀傷。<br />\n有認識詩敏及漢賢的朋友亦紛紛在fb發帖盼死者安息，並將其頭像轉為黑色悼念。一名親密女友人阿婷，更在fb上載一張自拍照，手背上紋有「2017.08.12」，日期為二人死忌，之後又留言稱：「也許我能做到只能如此，我懷念您們的所有，也許只有我們才知道彼此有多重要。」<br />\n阿婷又謂與詩敏約定要做一輩子的好朋友，永遠保護她。阿婷又說，當她發脾氣離家出走時，詩敏與漢賢曾整晚在街頭尋找，直言打從心底愛他們。對於二人突然離世感愕然，「您們走了，也留下我一個人，教我什（怎）學會撐下去，我恨我自己什（怎）麼沒把您2個人保護得更好」。<br />\n有詩敏的舊同事指她為人樂觀友善，「詩敏一路好走&hellip;&hellip;我哋下世再做朋友！」<br />\n■記者劉柏麟、溫瑞麟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有親友認屍後須人攙扶離開。詹家志攝<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t劏房火同室　違規住人　防煙門被拆屋宇署下令業主30日內還原<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"ad788c4dbe4a077520a2d7aecc78a59017d38932","tid":360142,"uid":389,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e3aa697f80d56645b922fa5004f5ba2f3608649","tid":360142,"uid":58099,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"懷念耶耶系列"},{"pid":"1edb1147054fa7a10cc9f6a9ba0766c70c56ec9d","tid":360142,"uid":1672,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896d3fb262a4e28c34d26b411fddd49257975d14","tid":360142,"uid":55597,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1kVeDJXXXXXbdaXXXq6xXFXXX7/Full-Metal-Alchemist-Dragon-Rhombus-Hexagon-Don-t-Forget-3-Oct-11-Chrome-Color-Belt-Chain.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fae01.alicdn.com%2Fkf%2FHTB1kVeDJXXXXXbdaXXXq6xXFXXX7%2FFull-Metal-Alchemist-Dragon-Rhombus-Hexagon-Don-t-Forget-3-Oct-11-Chrome-Color-Belt-Chain.jpg&h=b5159990&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39c58475a5cb479d599ff9dd2da0845e3181ddb0","tid":360142,"uid":116131,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"雖然我覺得個紋身可以設計得再好啲<br />\n不過如果係知己咁樣做真係好正常"},{"pid":"5c8256888a0d8896708d6b856f040a48beef10b4","tid":360142,"uid":1067,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1kVeDJXXXXXbdaXXXq6xXFXXX7/Full-Metal-Alchemist-Dragon-Rhombus-Hexagon-Don-t-Forget-3